Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.66,1:56:26.55,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不需要 拋棄掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.79,1:56:29.26,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在心裡 也不在腦海裡
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.51,1:56:32.77,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪都找不到的這份心意
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.95,1:56:35.94,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.15,1:56:38.99,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚地感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.23,1:56:43.93,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的環抱我的溫柔中前進
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.58,1:56:50.67,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.58,1:57:01.25,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於 遇上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光探測器確認
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光探測器同步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離接觸還剩下0021
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸艦 解除光學迷彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固定用臂連接開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我好等啊 琳達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個已經完成了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會來這裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是專為Twin Drive定制的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的GN粒子輸出裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了兩年也只製造出了這兩台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間和人手都不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高濃度粒子領域內
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以腦量子波進行意識共有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接戰鬥區域內每個人的思維
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了終結戰爭的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是剎那渴求的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 QAN[T]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友機 半數被擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握了地球聯邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖支配世界的獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都必須擊潰他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了用我們的雙手開創新時代！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 那個長頭髮的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府勢力卡塔隆之流 根本不是我們的對手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 世界會由我們A-LAWS統治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次實現永久的和平！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個想要根絕紛爭的私立武裝組織嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這根本沒有你出場的餘地！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將會由我們A-LAWS統一！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動 動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為由少數派把持的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是人們所期望的世界嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的天人 你們戰鬥的意義是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了瓦解你們那淪為傀儡的聯邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新政權已經開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了創造新世界 我們會戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們天人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raiser Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個電影是根據事實改編的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新政權的輿論宣傳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.64,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}怎麼看都是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.29,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有趣的嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美化得太過頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影不就是這樣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實可是沒有那麼美好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭是更可怕的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 好像你親眼見過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀨木小姐叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:37.60,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}天人的4名年輕人 拼上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:40.50,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}與4台Gundam一起奔赴戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:45.15,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}天人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒有出場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後 已經過了兩年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立武裝組織 天人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們所進行的武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給世界帶來了變革
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很緩慢 但正在走向一個沒有戰爭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對許許多多紛爭進行武力介入的天人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和做出了許多打壓行為的獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過武力給人們心中種下了恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的這種和平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在無法忘記的恐怖上建立起的虛假和平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們有必要去思考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留意這個變化中的世界 為了找到真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近看起來很穩定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有再發作了 差不多可以出院了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要著急 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間還很充裕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩年間 天人沒有出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在 怎樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說不能直接視察是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕索提婭議員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地的開發還在初期階段 有很多危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為中東使團代表的諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是發生什麼萬一的話 我們承擔不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人員大半都是因前政權的中東政策
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而強制移居殖民地的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們之中應該有人希望回歸祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們殖民地公社
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給工作人員提供符合聯邦法規定的工作環境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這份工作收入如此之高 不會有人想要離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼讓我們去視察也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經說過有危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視察就請在資源衛星宙域內進行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊的情況我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 能讓我見見工作人員和他們的家屬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想和他們直接談談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談話…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就安排一下去工作人員宿舍慰問的日程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 視察後會談上見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有政府做後盾…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管是政策改變還是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能失去那批勞動者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 這裡是宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微小的事情都有可能喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏離了視察路線了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在前往你們要求視察的工作人員宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然特意在資源衛星上建造宿舍？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼看待這個殖民地上的開發現場的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿足了聯邦法規定的勞動條件…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用你自己的話來說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中東的人民自不必說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望你能得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我家人幸福的話 我也覺得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長致各位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所屬不明的機動戰士接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為防萬一 請繫好安全帶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是殖民公社的機動戰士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙霧彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子？不過 這樣他也看不見！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鎖定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我來控制吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣做的話 你家人就能得到幸福了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把槍奪走！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動！你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊不成就搞暗殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民公社還真是亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無名無姓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin 1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行…者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去打個招呼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得有那種必要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這麼遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還虧他是個變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你也有自己的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此 才需要加深我們互相的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋求最好的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是通過鬥爭 而是通過對話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 沒想到天人居然還在持續活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們如今依然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和整個世界戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是敏銳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經成為一個好女人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了維塔的情報 事先阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟皇小姐報告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的遲鈍真是無可救藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣能幫上聯邦對殖民地的救濟的忙就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新政權建立才兩年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑣碎的事情唯有由我們來解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動Gundam的話就能成為世界的抑制力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在政府推行著融合政策的當下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也只能低調地行事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要安靜地存在著就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到特殊的時刻到來為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔發來的定期報告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍將進行對向地球圈飛來的探測船的拆除工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對探測船的拆除工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道是從哪飛來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從木星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那艘船的詳細資料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼在意的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到後告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞艾先生最近好神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那他已經成為了伊奧利亞·肖漢博格所提倡的新人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是感覺到了一些我們所不知道的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人所建造的外太空航行艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進出外太空…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人的創立者 伊奧利亞·肖漢博格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在三個世紀前就已經構思這個計劃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵查艦隊發來了關於接近地球圈的探測船的調查報告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船籍編號9374 船名歐羅巴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大約於一百三十多年前 出發去木星進行探索的船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船內部情況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有生命反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知偵查艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採用PLAN D34 使用粒子導彈攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變探測船的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是准將
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要過多少年你才會注意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好 過來當我的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要多學習學習才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准將親自到訪 實在榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設施的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 系統構造很獨特 非常複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又是如此之大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我們大概掌握了這艘船70%的構造
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子型運算處理系統 維塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這啥啊 臉長的一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是維塔的活體終端 原始變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始變革者？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔通過連接原始變革者來收集世界上的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並統轄和管理著這些信息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立武裝組織天人 之所以在七年前能做到那種程度的武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為有維塔給他們做支援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們也得到了這個系統的恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久 目標將進入導彈的射程範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達預定地點的同時 按照PLAN D34 開始粒子導彈攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵查艦隊發來的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到達地點 導彈發射準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過維塔確認的 純種變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛不說話 跟大佐打招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是准將
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是迪卡魯多·沙曼大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是傲慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被當做小白鼠來對待的話 連心都已經腐壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革者是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這種事都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不擅長讀報告書…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的變革者 簡單地說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是進化了的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握情況能力 空間認識能力 腦量子波增大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細胞改變導致肉體得到強化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論上我們認為他們有著比常人多一倍的壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在散佈著GN粒子的區域內
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以通過腦量子波來共享意識
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為變革者的出現 也在伊奧利亞的計劃之內嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我個人的觀點 應該是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN導彈全部命中目標
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認一下探測船的軌道改變率…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是這樣 我有這份確信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探測船的軌道改變率 不到預定中的20%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然處於奔向地球圈的軌道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經發射了足夠的粒子導彈的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在搞什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是想知道 變革者的實力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 會如你所願地使用新型機體出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 把我的思考…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是小白鼠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gadelaza
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以變革者的技術轉用而來的 我軍下一期的主力候補機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有著匹敵五個Mobile Suits小隊的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還能取得比這更好的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是沙曼大尉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波控制系統 沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gadelaza 迪卡魯多·沙曼 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子導彈第三波 全部命中目標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標仍然在衝入地球圈的軌道！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這船太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放棄啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為粒子量全都用在了推進器上 威力就…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友軍機？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波同步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN FANG 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平日的積憤 就讓我發洩出來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等的性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是變革者專用機的力量嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打散的探測船的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:24:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都在大氣層中燃燒殆盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您覺得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.02,0:24:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白軍隊期待沙曼大尉的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.94,0:24:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 給他作為大尉相應的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.31,0:24:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於拉格朗日3的視察事件
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從帕索提婭大使那得知受到了殖民公社的露骨妨礙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.62,0:24:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派軍隊進行護衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.50,0:24:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要是以武力進行威脅的話 就和前政權一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.55,0:24:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再給殖民公社發佈一次政府的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.84,0:24:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並準備回應文件
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.21,0:24:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不是有點太軟弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.46,0:24:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融合政策已經足夠了 過多讓步只會助長他們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.39,0:24:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融合政策的關鍵在於耐心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.11,0:24:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是太急躁的話會加大產生扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.03,0:24:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像天人那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.52,0:25:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊似乎已經成功消除了奔向地球圈的探測船
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.32,0:25:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有部分碎片掉落到了地面上…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.35,0:25:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據報告 是迪卡魯多·沙曼大尉的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.35,0:25:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙曼大尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.85,0:25:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一個被確認的變革者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.28,0:25:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究隊伍將大尉投入了實戰 想借此收集更多的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.09,0:25:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有向變革者進化可能性的人們 正在不停增加
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.10,0:25:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望他們能盡快確立他這樣一個模範樣本
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.41,0:25:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是變革者的數量增加的話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.72,0:25:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊時代人跟他們的能力差會暴露出來 就有可能產生衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.43,0:25:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們有必要加強基礎設施的建設
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.27,0:26:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行試驗進行得很順利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.31,0:26:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的預計在本月中將出廠
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.47,0:26:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？掉下來的探測船的碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.67,0:26:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 在那種情況下都沒燒掉是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.12,0:26:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要問這些
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.78,0:26:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說瑪奈金准將下達了調查命令
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.35,0:26:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息真靈通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.64,0:26:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事已經派出宇宙艦船去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.01,0:26:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我瞭解一些了再聯繫你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.23,0:26:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可靠的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.79,0:26:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探測船的碎片真的掉在這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.75,0:26:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親眼看見有光亮的 是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.28,0:26:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然政府說全部都在大氣層裡燒掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.77,0:26:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡 那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.86,0:27:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的調查隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.57,0:27:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然探測船的碎片在這
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.07,0:27:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是獨家新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.50,0:27:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.98,0:27:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.09,0:27:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快去叫救護車！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.61,0:27:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.73,0:28:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.01,0:28:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲她？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.84,0:28:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個 抱歉 我有急事…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.91,0:28:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.02,0:28:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.78,0:28:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.32,0:28:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.00,0:28:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.83,0:28:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.72,0:28:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.43,0:28:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.69,0:28:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.89,0:28:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.63,0:29:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒什麼值得大書特書的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.87,0:29:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜博士 能聽聽作為宇宙物理學者的你的意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.54,0:29:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這個碎片沒有在大氣層裡面燒掉 而落到了地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.89,0:29:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.08,0:29:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是因為探測船質量的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.12,0:29:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使受到了粒子導彈的攻擊 探測船的軌道也沒有大的改變
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.42,0:29:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由也是同樣如此
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.66,0:30:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 探測船有著我們無法想像的質量 也就是重量…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.71,0:30:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利～～
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.07,0:30:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來見我的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.36,0:30:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.05,0:30:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一如既往地這麼鬧騰啊 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.06,0:30:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們分析過碎片 但是只檢測出了微量的宇宙射線
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.07,0:30:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質的組成和構造與地球上的沒什麼不同
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.81,0:30:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很有深意的結果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.16,0:30:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.69,0:30:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收了的碎片還不到掉下來全部的20%
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.36,0:30:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是有人拿走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.37,0:30:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上 軍隊的回收班也遭到了損失
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.22,0:30:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 我還想到了兩個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.74,0:30:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是碎片自然毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.98,0:30:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是碎片自主移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.17,0:30:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自主移動？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.38,0:30:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.62,0:30:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種不科學的說法…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.30,0:30:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是比利
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.51,0:30:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.86,0:30:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是碎片的落下地點
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.50,0:31:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 這些是自從碎片落下後發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.73,0:31:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種奇怪事故的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.40,0:31:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼近…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.04,0:31:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如碎片移動了 它們到底要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.95,0:31:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我已經有假設了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.69,0:31:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能協助我驗證嗎 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.78,0:31:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.24,0:31:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府的絕密資料
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.85,0:31:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波極高 有擁有成為變革者的基因的市民資料數據庫
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.53,0:31:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到地上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.43,0:31:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情報說 掉到地上的碎片襲擊了腦量子波高的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.82,0:31:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真的可信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.44,0:31:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是維塔發來的確定資料
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.51,0:31:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的 我們同伴就有危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.41,0:31:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 請聯繫阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.35,0:31:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.09,0:31:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借用下小型艦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.16,0:31:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.66,0:31:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你去 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.21,0:31:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 無法聯繫上
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.85,0:31:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.29,0:31:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.65,0:32:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽光接收基地停止了供電
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.86,0:32:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事讓你這麼在意嗎 瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.78,0:32:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我總覺得說不出地不安
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.15,0:32:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 因為我的任性來讓你陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.18,0:32:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 偶爾繞繞遠路也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.96,0:32:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發電設施不見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.18,0:32:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.99,0:32:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.58,0:33:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.22,0:33:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.01,0:33:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒維小姐的PTSD
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.73,0:33:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即創傷後心理壓力緊張綜合症
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.01,0:33:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Post-traumatic stress disorder
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.32,0:33:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然恢復得很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.39,0:33:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這幾天的病情有點反覆
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.41,0:33:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道原因是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.71,0:33:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不太清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.22,0:33:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.25,0:33:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.42,0:33:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.15,0:33:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.82,0:33:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.34,0:34:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.15,0:34:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.09,0:34:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停電？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.18,0:34:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.57,0:34:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.73,0:34:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.82,0:34:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.77,0:34:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.43,0:34:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.84,0:34:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來！！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.79,0:34:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.90,0:34:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.05,0:35:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.97,0:35:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來！！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.91,0:35:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.78,0:35:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.90,0:35:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.19,0:35:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.77,0:35:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.42,0:35:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.63,0:35:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才只是威嚇
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.09,0:35:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不會手軟
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.32,0:35:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.43,0:35:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯·阿爾馬克！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.32,0:36:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它盯上的是瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.54,0:36:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不廢話嗎 是衝著瑪莉的腦量子波去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.71,0:36:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.82,0:36:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.00,0:36:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒工夫囉囉嗦嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.63,0:36:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體借我用了 搭檔！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.17,0:36:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.05,0:36:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所想
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.81,0:36:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然盯著我的腦量子波來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.21,0:36:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.17,0:37:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 這點彫蟲小技…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.58,0:37:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.14,0:37:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.65,0:37:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦 你的假期看來要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.97,0:38:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯·阿爾馬克！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.13,0:38:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.44,0:38:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.66,0:38:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底怎麼回事啊 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.07,0:38:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.70,0:39:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.22,0:39:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金中將
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.73,0:39:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦議會緊急派來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.51,0:39:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大總統特使 克勞斯·格拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.21,0:39:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.97,0:39:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.08,0:39:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.44,0:39:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.75,0:39:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只描述事實的話 實驗對像
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.36,0:39:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個少女的肉體組織的大約一半正在變成金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.82,0:39:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金屬？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.34,0:39:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球外變異性金屬體
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.29,0:39:47.95,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Extraterrestrial Living-metal Shapeshifter
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.29,0:39:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把這個外星體取名為「ELS」
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.41,0:39:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 在這裡的ELS已經停止活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.70,0:39:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無法掌握它的生命體構造
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.76,0:40:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 ELS有被能放出腦量子波的人類吸引的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.36,0:40:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 擁有成為變革者基因的人類 會被盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.90,0:40:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉德議員
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.66,0:40:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們去腦量子波屏蔽設施避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.51,0:40:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你向聯邦議會提案
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.16,0:40:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.42,0:40:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去安排
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.05,0:40:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 原因是落下的木星探測船的碎片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.66,0:40:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想比較正確吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.28,0:40:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事關重大
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.13,0:40:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人類和未知的存在接觸了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.65,0:40:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們無法掌握它們的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.94,0:40:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它和其他物體融合 並且急劇繁殖的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.87,0:40:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設立緊急對策局
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.77,0:40:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時 召集世界各地的科學家
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.21,0:40:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與維塔合作 開始分析變異性金屬體
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.62,0:40:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報洩露的風險如何
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.37,0:40:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡上已經由維塔進行信息管制了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.53,0:41:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請求媒體進行合作了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.98,0:41:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷疑與事件有關的東西 都已經交給軍隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.69,0:41:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洩露的風險應該很低
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.94,0:41:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都看我們的對應了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.62,0:41:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們盡最大的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.14,0:41:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈普狄斯姆先生 皮瑞斯小姐 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.32,0:41:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給人的感覺變了好多啊 米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.96,0:41:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個髮型很適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.42,0:41:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在向成熟女性邁進嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.32,0:41:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特也是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.43,0:41:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.79,0:41:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.72,0:41:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.54,0:41:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛斯洛特他們怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.59,0:41:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由聯邦政府安排 去腦量子波屏蔽設施避難了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.77,0:41:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是新政府
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.25,0:41:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很正確的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.78,0:41:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 我拜託你的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.19,0:41:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個事情的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.29,0:41:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說那之前 先讓我喘口氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.52,0:41:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.89,0:42:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那0012在簡報室集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.15,0:42:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白～
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.25,0:42:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞你們也休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.99,0:42:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間還是老樣子留在那
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.85,0:42:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.82,0:42:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.16,0:42:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.19,0:42:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來帶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.74,0:42:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.46,0:42:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會見
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.45,0:42:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.31,0:42:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.92,0:42:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.32,0:42:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感覺到什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.23,0:42:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.13,0:42:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很難用言語表達
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.02,0:42:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意剎那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.67,0:42:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.23,0:42:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從剎那變成了變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.48,0:42:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎又變回了剛認識時候的那個他
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.20,0:42:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對著誰都不會敞開心扉的那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.90,0:43:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對變化了的自己感到很困惑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.93,0:43:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那種能力也是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.12,0:43:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他強烈地意識到了他和我們是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.57,0:43:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能為剎那做點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.27,0:43:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去感受他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.33,0:43:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受…他？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.08,0:43:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.24,0:43:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了互相理解而必須的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.91,0:43:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是不斷和他擦身而過
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.85,0:43:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不去持續地感受的話
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.38,0:43:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份心情是不會傳達給他的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.14,0:43:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強烈的思念 將人們維繫在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.02,0:43:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了真正意義上能互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.70,0:43:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.08,0:43:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.42,0:43:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.68,0:43:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.80,0:44:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在想事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.89,0:44:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.93,0:44:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真如這個報告書所說
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.30,0:44:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探測船裡混進了未知金屬體的話
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.68,0:44:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那同樣的事情就有可能再次發生
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.42,0:44:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種偶然 不會再出現的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.66,0:44:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出現的話 那地球就完全被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.71,0:44:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被壞蛋宇宙人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.67,0:44:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你在一起的時候 總覺得如果認真地思考問題就像傻瓜一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.46,0:44:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.23,0:44:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.98,0:44:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個設施的一部分 自行運轉起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.81,0:44:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.80,0:44:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星側面 未確認的艙門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.32,0:44:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把影像傳過來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.58,0:44:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.20,0:44:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.02,0:45:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那所看到的裡本斯·阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.66,0:45:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個人物的真身
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.30,0:45:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大約130年前進行的木星載人探測計劃的船員
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.22,0:45:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.13,0:45:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.48,0:45:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星載人探測計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.91,0:45:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了暗地裡開發GN-DRIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.25,0:45:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有裡本斯型的變革者也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.29,0:45:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.35,0:45:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被金屬外星體吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.41,0:45:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想是對的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.05,0:45:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔的情報說 地上似乎也發生了同樣的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.76,0:45:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星體的目的到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.96,0:45:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.06,0:45:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 我們甚至連它們有沒意識都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.34,0:45:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E-SENSOR有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.68,0:45:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有東西向本艦靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.90,0:46:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光學望遠鏡 最大倍數進行顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.37,0:46:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的運輸船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.29,0:46:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.14,0:46:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.20,0:46:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過外形推測出相應的船體
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.46,0:46:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.61,0:46:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最相似的是船籍編號9374
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.18,0:46:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星載人探測船？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.63,0:46:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歐羅巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.78,0:46:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.18,0:46:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼被破壞了的船會…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.40,0:46:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.92,0:46:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.66,0:46:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一 第二 第三艙門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.72,0:46:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁彈射器 全數值上升
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.05,0:46:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈射時間 交給斯特拉特斯先生你控制
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.70,0:46:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.72,0:46:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Zabanya
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.77,0:46:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.26,0:46:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始狙擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.21,0:46:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.81,0:46:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.82,0:47:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果剛才的話是真的 我也被外星體盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.64,0:47:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不能給船上的人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.28,0:47:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.24,0:47:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈射準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.98,0:47:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.09,0:47:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Halute
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.18,0:47:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞·哈普狄斯姆 索瑪·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.38,0:47:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始迎擊行動
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.52,0:47:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 我想你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.94,0:47:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser是用粒子存儲器代替了太陽爐的應急用機體
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.87,0:47:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.72,0:47:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.73,0:47:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.76,0:47:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.83,0:47:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.95,0:47:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.72,0:47:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.80,0:48:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在增加 在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.42,0:48:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道你們有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.54,0:48:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能讓你們從這過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.77,0:48:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 外星體盯上了瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.58,0:48:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.48,0:48:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導彈被…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.12,0:48:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.59,0:48:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.97,0:48:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人接近 敵人接近
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.87,0:48:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.64,0:48:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 脫離戰場了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.45,0:48:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.71,0:48:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.94,0:49:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.72,0:49:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.08,0:49:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.72,0:49:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.07,0:50:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.12,0:50:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.89,0:50:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾莉艾卡小姐 那個機體是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.10,0:51:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來幫我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.16,0:51:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各機 集中進行對飛向地球圈的碎片的清除工作
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.61,0:51:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.61,0:51:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.85,0:51:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.89,0:51:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.13,0:51:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.86,0:51:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為原始變革者的我 可以把意識複製到活體終端裡
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.80,0:51:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒空享受重逢的喜悅了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.25,0:51:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.70,0:51:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不攻擊ELS
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.52,0:51:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.57,0:51:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 聯邦政府把外星體稱為ELS
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.41,0:51:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.59,0:51:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你不攻擊ELS的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.21,0:51:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.36,0:51:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說不知道…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.69,0:51:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 看來是作為變革者的直覺告訴你要這樣做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.70,0:52:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔的情報系統也無法弄清ELS的行動目的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.24,0:52:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你從它們那感覺到了什麼 而下意識地做出了反應
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.17,0:52:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 ELS是有意志的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.71,0:52:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然ELS又要再次向地球圈襲來…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.16,0:52:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟ELS戰鬥的是天人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.09,0:52:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然政府管制了信息
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.64,0:52:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.12,0:52:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想著以前的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.49,0:52:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…才…才沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.38,0:52:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這個 你是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.02,0:52:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS有智慧…也就是有意志嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.30,0:52:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.35,0:52:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.32,0:52:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星發射出的特有電波
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.29,0:52:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是俗稱的「木星電波」 你知道這種東西存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.37,0:52:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.82,0:53:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 那個電波產生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.35,0:53:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然微弱 但是能發現腦量子波的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.25,0:53:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.09,0:53:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 從木星發來了信息？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.77,0:53:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.07,0:53:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那點我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.25,0:53:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星體…ELS的來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.68,0:53:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那個伊奧利亞大叔說的「即將到來的對話」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.27,0:53:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃中提到的「即將到來的對話」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.47,0:53:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的是從人類能進出宇宙後開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.77,0:53:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是數個世紀後的事情 怎麼會是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.78,0:53:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.21,0:53:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類明明還完全沒有做好準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.73,0:53:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實逼人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.96,0:53:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.04,0:53:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也贊同這個意見
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.12,0:53:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現狀是我們這邊已經遭受損失了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.45,0:53:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種想法太魯莽了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.41,0:53:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 或許是因為ELS還不瞭解我們才會這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.96,0:53:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那是怎麼想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.04,0:54:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那你是怎麼想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.48,0:54:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.76,0:54:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.63,0:54:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.27,0:54:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他感覺到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.21,0:54:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.27,0:54:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔的情報中提到的 00 QAN[T]的情況如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.17,0:54:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安他們正在抓緊建造中
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.40,0:54:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照剎那所希望造的那個機體 或許是我們的殺手鑭
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.67,0:54:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要和ELS…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.63,0:54:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也考慮過才對
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.38,0:54:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們太依靠剎那了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.53,0:54:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.77,0:54:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久疏問候了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.63,0:54:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.90,0:54:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們和其他的科學家一起 在這裡研究ELS
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.11,0:55:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您給了我親眼看到ELS的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.69,0:55:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為地面上的情況似乎也平靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.68,0:55:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您叫我嗎 瑪奈金准將
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.59,0:55:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.43,0:55:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是迪卡魯多·沙曼大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.60,0:55:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.83,0:55:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你的資料看過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.41,0:55:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.17,0:55:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對變質了的木星電波的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.72,0:55:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拜託一介士兵做這麼難的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.09,0:55:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是那麼地萬能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.72,0:55:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們對ELS的情報是壓倒性地不足
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.65,0:55:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少也好 希望能給點線索
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.35,0:55:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.33,0:55:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是「呼喊」
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.67,0:55:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喊？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.90,0:55:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在呼叫我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.71,0:55:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查那個 是你們諸位的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.49,0:55:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.44,0:56:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劣等種…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.04,0:56:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.17,0:56:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.72,0:56:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.74,0:56:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.86,0:56:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.10,0:56:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.40,0:56:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.99,0:56:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.24,0:56:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.75,0:56:41.20,eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(843,990)}Ganymede
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.75,0:56:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木衛三被消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.20,0:56:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星大紅斑處產生了巨大的重力場
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.25,0:56:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星環破壞 被逐漸吸收進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.69,0:56:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大紅斑的中心 半徑6萬公里的雲層被向中心吸去！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.81,0:56:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道電梯上的天文台也發來了同樣的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.85,0:56:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信 木星居然出現了巨大的洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.13,0:56:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.55,0:57:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS的大軍…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.54,0:57:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.02,0:57:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.06,0:57:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.53,0:57:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計算ELS到達地球圈的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.97,0:57:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.85,0:57:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.26,0:57:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離到達地球圈 還有95日
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.10,0:57:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有三個月…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.63,0:57:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是留給我們與「即將到來的對話」的時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.64,0:58:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.31,0:58:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.37,0:58:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算呆在這裡 什麼都不會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.39,0:58:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.00,0:58:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從木星 與大紅斑發生變異同時出現的謎之外星體 通稱ELS
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.71,0:58:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們雖然正在向太陽系中心移動
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.80,0:58:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是基本不會到達地球圈
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.49,0:58:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要被推測和謠言所蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.63,0:58:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請市民們進行適當的活動…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.39,0:58:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說萬一 有到達地球圈的機率嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.83,0:58:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.98,0:58:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果那樣的話 從ELS的移動速度考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.53,0:58:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.53,0:58:37.95,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}大約九十天後會到達地球
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.91,0:58:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.27,0:58:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.27,0:58:41.94,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}如果移動速度加快 時間還會減少
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.98,0:58:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.39,0:58:43.80,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}時間非常緊迫
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.10,0:58:47.97,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這三個月時間內 世界都將關注聯邦政府的對應…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.06,0:58:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼有外星人從木星襲來 不過是個幻想而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.45,0:58:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是外星人 是變異性金屬體
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.35,0:58:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來咬文嚼字！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.55,0:58:54.61,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是什麼都無所謂！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.46,0:58:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載人探測船有可能是ELS的先遣部隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.90,0:58:58.51,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.48,0:59:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能保證我們不會被盯上麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.27,0:59:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在不是說木星來物體不會來地球圈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.59,0:59:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 難道沒有改變軌道的可能性嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.02,0:59:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的金屬能做到這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.80,0:59:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上載人探測船不是已經掉到地球上了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.73,0:59:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不來都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.72,0:59:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能對市民提出怎樣的應對方案才是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.90,0:59:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增強軍備！先下手為強！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.89,0:59:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外沒有保護市民的辦法了！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.64,0:59:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋！你想否定現政權的融合政策嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.46,0:59:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加無謂的預算的話 不就會招致反對聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.06,0:59:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳 面對地球的頭等大事還想明哲保身嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.22,0:59:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才混帳！這麼想打仗嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.56,0:59:38.60,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}可惡 你這個懦弱的保守派！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.39,0:59:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論提出什麼方案 都無法消除市民的危機感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.01,0:59:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下一代的MS的列裝 也變得容易了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.36,0:59:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明終於能進行對話 就能讓人民回到祖國了…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.39,0:59:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.57,0:59:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.57,1:00:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議會的情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.27,1:00:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從克勞斯那裡聽說 好像比預想中的分歧更大
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.86,1:00:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能理解持樂觀態度的人們啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.12,1:00:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟說從木星襲來的外星體盯上了地球什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.64,1:00:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們做好自己能做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.33,1:00:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.67,1:00:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備庇護所 儲備食物 抑止恐慌…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.04,1:00:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就期待瑪麗娜大人的領導力了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.03,1:00:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在融合政策下
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.53,1:00:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不滿削減軍費
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.13,1:00:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官 以現有的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.77,1:00:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以應付ELS到何種程度？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.78,1:00:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白地說
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.29,1:00:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為ELS的能力和規模都還是未知數 所以無法回答
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.13,1:00:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說我的個人意見的話
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.94,1:00:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望它們能像推測那樣只是擦過地球就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.58,1:00:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是絕望的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.38,1:00:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS可是有被腦量子波吸引的特性
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.68,1:00:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以量子型運算系統維塔
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.49,1:00:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能會被襲擊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.11,1:01:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前派出的調查艦隊怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.10,1:01:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計在16日後
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.33,1:01:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在火星圈附近捕捉到ELS
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.52,1:01:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果目標真是具有意志的話
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.43,1:01:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能確認它們的真正意圖
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.32,1:01:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪卡魯多大尉也編入在隊伍裡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.05,1:01:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把變革者也編入？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.09,1:01:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說ELS會被腦量子波吸引嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.29,1:01:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.71,1:01:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將大尉強大的腦量子波作為誘餌
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.35,1:01:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變ELS的前進路線
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.00,1:01:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會被人譴責說不人道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.27,1:01:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是有著要守護60億以上生命的義務
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.66,1:01:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉是軍人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.36,1:01:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是為了保護大量的民眾的話
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.54,1:01:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該非常樂意地完成任務才是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.32,1:01:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM 完成
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.22,1:01:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩艘火星駐紮艦船已經完成補給
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.82,1:01:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 在全部匯合的同時
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.79,1:01:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦隊將轉而進行與ELS的接觸行動
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.58,1:01:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.25,1:01:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中將 可以問你一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.05,1:01:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？說來看看
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.73,1:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中將為什麼會自願參加這個危險的行動呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.06,1:02:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道「俄羅斯的荒熊」吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.13,1:02:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的是塞魯哥·斯米盧諾夫大佐吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.91,1:02:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.03,1:02:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常瞭解他的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.29,1:02:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他雖然只是一介軍人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.63,1:02:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是個一直考慮著軍隊走向和人類未來的男子漢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.21,1:02:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我一生都疲於出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.22,1:02:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次遇上人類的危機
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.50,1:02:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想試一次用他那樣的生存方式活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.49,1:02:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gadelaza GN-X 全部機體已經出發
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.81,1:02:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知各部隊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.98,1:02:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗試與ELS接觸
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.29,1:02:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看對方有什麼反應…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.83,1:02:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移到PLAN 31
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.68,1:02:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只觀察對方反應的話無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.21,1:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS的真正意圖 就讓我去弄清楚吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.51,1:02:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gadelaza先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.16,1:02:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他去 這樣也能知道敵人的真正意圖
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.62,1:03:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在移動嗎 那就讓我來會會你
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.44,1:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群怪物！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.57,1:03:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子裡面…響個不停啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.51,1:03:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不停叫喊啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.78,1:03:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦先遣部隊在火星附近與ELS接觸
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.00,1:04:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已經進入戰鬥狀態
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.28,1:04:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS被吞噬了？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.66,1:04:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.09,1:04:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將ELS確定為人類的敵對勢力
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.08,1:04:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人 向本艦接近！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.87,1:04:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上迎擊！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.19,1:04:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導彈也被吞噬了！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.78,1:04:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS正從左舷入侵！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.24,1:04:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司 司令！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.69,1:04:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.42,1:04:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦的物質構造正在改變！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.92,1:04:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.86,1:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ELS干的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.57,1:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變污染還在擴大 無法停止！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.42,1:05:02.98,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}無法控制了！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.06,1:05:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 去救生艇
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.48,1:05:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大型體過來了！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.99,1:05:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想承認…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.92,1:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…居然是事實…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.61,1:05:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母艦被吞噬了？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.24,1:05:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒打算死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.12,1:05:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要將你們一網打盡！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.44,1:05:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不算殺自己人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.74,1:06:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.29,1:06:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳！！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.15,1:06:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的艦隊…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.04,1:06:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.45,1:06:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們到底想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.20,1:06:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再想吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.00,1:06:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.81,1:07:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.37,1:07:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊！快點！
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.63,1:07:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的機師…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.32,1:07:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機停止攻擊 馬上撤退
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.74,1:07:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會用Raiser System
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.93,1:07:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造高濃度GN粒子的意識共有領域
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.43,1:07:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要用那個機子來進行TRANS-AM？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.80,1:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.70,1:07:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raiser System啟動
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.09,1:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raiser System啟動
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.68,1:08:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算和ELS進行對話嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.76,1:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.05,1:08:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底為了什麼來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.20,1:08:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.37,1:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 你們的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.76,1:08:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam 正在被ELS侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.99,1:09:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊回收剎那 後退到Point Y32
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.43,1:09:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.31,1:09:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量太多了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.36,1:09:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.22,1:09:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00已經用光所有粒子了！
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.98,1:09:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee！
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.94,1:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是可以用腦量子波的！
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.17,1:10:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞！
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.94,1:10:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.26,1:10:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.13,1:10:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對話 剎那不能倒在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.35,1:11:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收剎那了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.38,1:11:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上用TRANS-AM回托勒密
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.61,1:11:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.64,1:11:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.38,1:11:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯！
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.78,1:11:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.61,1:11:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.55,1:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意後方 注意後方
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.59,1:11:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.63,1:12:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮游盾展開 浮游盾展開
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.62,1:12:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SolBrave小隊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.88,1:12:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以標準機動方式同時散開
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.29,1:12:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是復仇戰！
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.29,1:12:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全機 全速前進！
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.29,1:12:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam已經撤退了麼
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.28,1:12:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機 避免與對方的接觸
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.34,1:13:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.87,1:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐！ELS它們…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.57,1:13:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們到底在圖謀什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.36,1:13:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將進行粒子擾亂
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.90,1:14:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將從當前宙域撤退
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.84,1:14:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.76,1:14:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在DFT223會合
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.70,1:14:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經將塞艾先生收治在醫療箱裡了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.58,1:14:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 發射粒子擾亂導彈
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.07,1:14:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收所有MS的同時
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.87,1:14:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個宙域脫離
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.10,1:14:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.38,1:14:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那！
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.63,1:15:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你們提供粒子補充
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.57,1:15:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是對你們幫助的回禮
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.82,1:15:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 即使你們已經全速趕來
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.99,1:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的同伴也已經全部戰死了 真是非常遺憾
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.52,1:15:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.74,1:15:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎麼可以這麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.44,1:15:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我而言 肉體只不過是容器而已
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.64,1:15:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那個時候除那以外別無他法
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.88,1:15:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我剎那現在的情況
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.52,1:15:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他打算和ELS共享意識的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.16,1:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法停止接收對方龐大的信息量
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.81,1:15:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦細胞受到了損傷
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.08,1:15:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經用了腦細胞再生裝置
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.02,1:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有可能會留下意識和記憶上的損傷
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.74,1:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.32,1:15:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 剎那的腦量子波
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.40,1:15:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能超出我們的想像的話
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.49,1:15:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能作為真正的變革者覺醒的話
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.28,1:15:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定能…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.34,1:16:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷地摸索人與人互相理解的道路
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.80,1:16:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對方是ELS也一樣想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.19,1:16:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了開拓未來
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.39,1:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的戰鬥吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.31,1:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.96,1:16:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個曾經為了超越Gundam而反覆做蠢事的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.00,1:16:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我那個想法果然是錯的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.17,1:16:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要超越的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.56,1:16:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個少年
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.42,1:16:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒有趕得及救援友軍
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.79,1:16:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也沒能救下這個少年
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.36,1:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.36,1:16:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.31,1:16:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告說木星出現了新的ELS
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.73,1:16:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補給完成後 我們馬上返回母艦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.31,1:17:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從木星出現的新的大型外星體
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.53,1:17:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直徑大約三千公里
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.28,1:17:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小與月球相當
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.33,1:17:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕 會向地球襲來
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.83,1:17:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上制定對策
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.39,1:17:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日 從木星出現的新的物體
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.14,1:17:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被認定為大型的ELS
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.73,1:17:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直徑大約和月球一樣 從規模看來
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.94,1:17:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽系各處 特別是火星
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.44,1:17:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及地球圈 會受到影響
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.88,1:17:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位市民請依照各機構的指示…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.97,1:17:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.64,1:17:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參謀總長從保密線路發來通信
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.49,1:17:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.81,1:17:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民的保護和媒體的應對都已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.36,1:17:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12小時後 將開始市民的避難
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.04,1:17:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.32,1:17:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們真有辦法對付那麼大的物體嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.13,1:18:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在事情已經發生了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.41,1:18:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們唯有做出對應
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.68,1:18:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須保護市民…保護這個星球
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.95,1:18:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.05,1:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩琳
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.12,1:18:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府的對策已經決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.96,1:18:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在議會正討論中
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.45,1:18:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 軍隊的行動似乎也變得匆忙起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.31,1:18:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.38,1:18:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.65,1:18:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入全部現有戰鬥力 展開絕對防衛線
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.72,1:18:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要阻止ELS入侵地球圈
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.56,1:18:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最前線的 是作為主力攻擊部隊投入的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.00,1:18:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一到第三艦隊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.66,1:18:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中心將配置第五到第九艦隊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.90,1:18:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的部隊將作為護衛 在司令部正面展開
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.37,1:18:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰司令官為凱蒂·瑪奈金准將
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.39,1:18:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經去進行集結參與這次作戰的部隊的工作了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.51,1:19:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有 准將正在視察的外太空航行艦已經完成舾裝
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.00,1:19:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將作為前線司令部參加本次作戰
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.99,1:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以參與作戰的全部艦隊在絕對防衛線上的集合
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.90,1:19:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定將在8765完成
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.84,1:19:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 可以做的事情就已經全部做完了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.78,1:19:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果ELS改變路線
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.71,1:19:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開了絕對防衛線的話又會如何
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.99,1:19:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地球就會受到毀滅性的打擊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.25,1:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說唯有向神祈禱了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.57,1:19:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是向神 而是要我們自己去努力
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.33,1:19:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了活下來 為了開拓未來
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.05,1:19:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算最終要傷害到他人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.32,1:19:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位市民
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.72,1:19:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府正對接近地球的大型ELS做出適當的對應
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.89,1:19:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不用擔心地面上會有危險
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.34,1:19:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為防萬一 請各位前往掩體避難
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.09,1:19:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要著急 保持冷靜 互相幫助地行動
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.56,1:19:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.71,1:19:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩體已經無法再容納更多的人了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.17,1:19:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣場上有很多無處安身的市民
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.54,1:20:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去可能會引發暴動
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.41,1:20:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算開放皇宮的所有設施
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.14,1:20:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請讓全體市民去避難
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.14,1:20:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人 您也請去避難…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.97,1:20:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.41,1:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要等到市民們都平安無事才去
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.74,1:20:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然政府選擇了戰鬥這條路啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.55,1:20:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是我支持大總統的判斷
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.25,1:20:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所期望的和平
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.95,1:20:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要人類能繼續生存下去 才能實現
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.00,1:20:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先必須保住性命 生存下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.27,1:20:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 我會拿起槍
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.59,1:20:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right All right
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.21,1:20:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 無需著急
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.72,1:20:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢慢前進
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.78,1:20:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府為了保護軌道電梯
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.00,1:20:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在招募能幫忙的技術人員
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.10,1:20:57.54,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}所有參加者 必須持有宇宙技師第一種執照
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.62,1:20:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.95,1:21:02.55,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}願意協助的人 請到指定的軍方設施進行簡單面試
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.77,1:21:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會去的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.55,1:21:04.78,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}然後決定分配到指定位置
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.32,1:21:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.97,1:21:06.53,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}工作地點 待遇
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.96,1:21:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.59,1:21:07.57,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}薪酬等條件
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.52,1:21:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你 我都想保護
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.73,1:21:13.23,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}都記載在聯邦政府網絡內的「宇宙技師招募」上
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.34,1:21:14.79,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}敬請查閱
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.71,1:21:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.03,1:21:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.63,1:21:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始後 就沒有我們能做的事情了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.19,1:21:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從ELS的行動推測
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.82,1:21:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們應該是打算和異種同化
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.05,1:21:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以和對方共享知識和意志了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.63,1:21:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了在膨脹了的個體內共享意識
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.86,1:21:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波是必須的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.81,1:21:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 它們會被持有變革者基因的人所吸引…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.17,1:21:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米…米娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.28,1:21:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候你在做什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.28,1:21:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在這種時期 才需要互相理解啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.29,1:21:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS也是一樣 會將自己接觸到的東西改變
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.55,1:22:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是可以改變的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.57,1:22:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的感情也是的…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.39,1:22:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請你溫柔點…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.65,1:22:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.87,1:22:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子剩餘量為零 推進器分離
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.90,1:22:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會到達匯合點
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.54,1:22:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS 距離到達地球圈
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.70,1:22:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約還有四千萬公里
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.98,1:22:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…還有大約七天嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.65,1:22:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有什麼要做的嗎 皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.61,1:22:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.86,1:22:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.07,1:22:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那個 需要剎那的恢復 以及…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.56,1:22:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.83,1:22:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個機體是…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.25,1:22:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.76,1:22:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GNT-0000
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.97,1:22:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體名 00 QAN[T]
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.69,1:22:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是變革者…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.65,1:23:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是剎那的專用機
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.81,1:23:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有超高濃度粒子
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.42,1:23:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說意識共有率得到了顯著提升
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.89,1:23:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.27,1:23:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說剎那的腦袋受傷了？！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.37,1:23:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.81,1:23:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都把QAN[T]帶來了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.87,1:23:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個機體會派上用場的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.00,1:23:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信剎那會恢復過來
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.00,1:23:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QAN[T]的最終調整就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.94,1:23:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有事想拜託你們
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.13,1:23:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.19,1:23:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德先生！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.51,1:23:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安 請你把維塔的小型終端
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.55,1:23:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安裝到QAN[T]上
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.99,1:23:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？你打算做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.35,1:23:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用維塔來控制ELS傳來的信息
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.39,1:23:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 GN-DRIVE 維塔 變革者
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.86,1:23:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·肖漢博格所追求的這三個東西
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.31,1:23:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了實現「即將到來的對話」
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.59,1:23:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.94,1:23:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.19,1:23:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們唯有盡力做到最好了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.38,1:23:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那也要盡快恢復
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.37,1:23:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇通知所有人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.65,1:24:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用TRANS-AM做最大加速
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.32,1:24:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備進行與ELS的接觸
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.69,1:24:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 這是天人的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.99,1:24:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我們剩下的最後任務
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.72,1:24:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨型ELS 距離還有1000
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.88,1:24:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有0032 將進入長距離導彈的射程範圍
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.00,1:24:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來 第一個賭局是我們贏了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.78,1:24:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.46,1:24:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各艦 當目標進入射程範圍後
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.29,1:24:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.96,1:24:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免粒子導彈和ELS接觸
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.12,1:24:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要設置成近爆引信
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.09,1:24:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就算被吞噬了也不怕
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.46,1:24:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出擊了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.33,1:25:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說了多少次是准將了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.07,1:25:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不準死
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.22,1:25:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.66,1:25:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各艦隊 長距離導彈發射準備 完成
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.89,1:25:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.67,1:25:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體第一波導彈攻擊 開始！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.96,1:25:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導彈 發射！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.98,1:25:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離目標還有370！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.25,1:25:30.51,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}第一波導彈攻擊已經全部完成發射
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.51,1:25:32.90,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}已確認艦隊向東面散開
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.74,1:25:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達300後啟動起爆系統
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.36,1:25:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,300！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.86,1:25:34.00,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GN粒子壓縮率…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.04,1:25:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認啟動！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.92,1:25:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全彈已起爆！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.17,1:25:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全彈命中！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.68,1:25:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS健在！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.18,1:25:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們似乎展開了某種防護盾！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.20,1:25:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.10,1:25:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然分析出了我們GN粒子場的特性…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.22,1:26:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型粒子炮 準備發射！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.71,1:26:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓MS小隊開始近距離作戰！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.56,1:26:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體MS準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.77,1:26:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為防止ELS的侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.12,1:26:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機打開防護盾作戰！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.97,1:26:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥力差距大約是一萬比一
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.80,1:26:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況很糟
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.61,1:26:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我一定會守護的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.38,1:26:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽所期待的世界！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.31,1:26:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙魯佈雷夫小隊的精英們聽好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.22,1:26:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下去要前往的戰場
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.98,1:26:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是需要諸位拼上性命的地方！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.81,1:26:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大家記住
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.58,1:26:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許死！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.18,1:26:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.60,1:26:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型粒子炮 充電率70%
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.65,1:26:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充電率90%
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.43,1:26:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充電率100%
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.64,1:26:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始掃射
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.99,1:26:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始掃射！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.45,1:27:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊 在用粒子炮攻擊的同時
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.83,1:27:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS隊也進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.29,1:27:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改為進行掃蕩作戰！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.69,1:27:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會被幹掉的！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.64,1:27:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死…我也要回去！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.10,1:27:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到大佐身邊！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.79,1:28:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？那是…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.77,1:28:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS正在逐一變成MS！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.88,1:28:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為融合之後得到了我們的情報嗎…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.77,1:28:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話 那這邊的武器也…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.17,1:28:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.90,1:28:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.87,1:28:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌張！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.53,1:28:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說 對手是Gundam級別的話…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.36,1:29:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅岡！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.75,1:29:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你答應過我的…！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.93,1:29:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 Point 336那裡…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.37,1:29:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.30,1:29:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連巡洋艦都有了嗎…！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.16,1:29:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩艘巡洋艦失去聯絡！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.22,1:29:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即重整陣形！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.68,1:29:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充電還要多少時間
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.01,1:29:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有55%的火力 發射！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.54,1:29:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,削弱敵方氣勢！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.24,1:29:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子炮 向Point24發射！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.19,1:29:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然將光束折射了？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.61,1:29:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們在學習…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.61,1:30:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三艦隊 被突破了！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.46,1:30:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去支援！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.80,1:30:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你們過去的！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.60,1:30:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？那些粒子光束是…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.25,1:30:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始進行阻止ELS侵略的行動
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.80,1:30:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.68,1:30:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由是什麼都不重要
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.20,1:30:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去幹就可以了！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.79,1:30:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算剎那來不了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.93,1:30:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會全力地狙擊！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.39,1:30:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊！狙擊！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.94,1:30:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮游炮展開 浮游炮展開
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.66,1:31:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天人
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.57,1:31:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zabanya Harute 已經加入戰場了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.64,1:31:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 開始炮擊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.54,1:31:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.82,1:31:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安 調整如何了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.88,1:31:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.39,1:31:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那！
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.48,1:32:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量上完全被壓制了！
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.23,1:32:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能放棄啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.21,1:32:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳啊！！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.73,1:33:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊被ELS逐一突破了！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.52,1:33:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.91,1:33:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS已經突破了第七艦隊！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.41,1:33:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓MS小隊去追擊！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.25,1:33:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們艦隊的損失多少
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.21,1:33:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之三十
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.80,1:33:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼短時間內就…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.08,1:33:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.13,1:33:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型炮台被ELS污染了！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.82,1:33:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞被污染機械 防止擴大！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.65,1:33:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 如此重要的武器…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.90,1:33:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS 突破絕對防衛線了！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.06,1:33:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你們過去的！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.81,1:34:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護市民
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.60,1:34:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是聯邦軍的軍人！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.72,1:35:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.79,1:35:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Point 13有ELS的巡洋艦接近！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.44,1:35:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉賽！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.28,1:35:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.80,1:35:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.34,1:36:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還在拚命活下去呢
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.69,1:36:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還要改變世界
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.01,1:36:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧 剎那
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.01,1:36:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要改變
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.88,1:36:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替沒有能改變的我
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.09,1:36:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.40,1:36:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 你…還活著啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.68,1:36:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.18,1:36:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那他？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.13,1:36:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.43,1:37:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.23,1:37:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.47,1:37:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用00 QAN[T]出擊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.01,1:37:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.18,1:37:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德先生的意識資料
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.73,1:37:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經傳送到QAN[T]的終端了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.80,1:37:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.42,1:37:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德先生
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.67,1:37:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜我 不管愛德先生變成什麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.23,1:37:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都最喜歡愛德先生了！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.16,1:37:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥？！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.30,1:37:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 太好了 找到個好男人了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.85,1:37:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.65,1:37:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.44,1:37:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事你不該笑的吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.93,1:37:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QAN[T]出擊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.26,1:37:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把話題扯開
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.69,1:37:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.41,1:37:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.70,1:37:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去剎那身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.76,1:37:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.77,1:37:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.53,1:37:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個人的愛太大了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.24,1:37:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要想念著那個人…就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.59,1:38:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS再次突破防衛線
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.76,1:38:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zabanya Harute 正在迎戰
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.60,1:38:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三艙門打開
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.92,1:38:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 QAN[T] 準備彈射
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.81,1:38:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.52,1:38:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線性同步電機電壓上升 突破730
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.90,1:38:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈射控制權交給剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.07,1:38:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 00 QAN[T]
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.03,1:38:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.27,1:38:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊！
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.97,1:38:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白虎號去掩護密蘇里號
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.73,1:38:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕特利庫
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.60,1:38:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我被困住了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.54,1:39:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像因為我太幸福了 不死身就沒了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.97,1:39:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上脫出啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.56,1:39:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.63,1:39:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不會就這麼死掉的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.20,1:39:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有這一隻 我也要跟它同歸於盡！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.97,1:39:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.75,1:39:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.61,1:39:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你好久了 少年！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.30,1:39:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.31,1:39:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對話 我們要去到ELS的中樞
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.42,1:39:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.26,1:39:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交給我吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.90,1:39:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了 哈羅！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.97,1:39:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.28,1:39:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到的就攻擊吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.43,1:40:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧 這就是反射和思考的結合！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.42,1:40:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.53,1:40:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.13,1:40:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.08,1:40:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.60,1:40:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵的力量啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.89,1:40:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這是開拓未來的力量！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.00,1:40:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.58,1:40:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.99,1:41:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這裡不是為了戰鬥的！
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.31,1:41:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.72,1:41:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要為了生存而戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.75,1:41:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是你嗎！
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.66,1:41:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算矛盾變大了也要生存下去
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.44,1:41:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…才叫做生存！
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.36,1:41:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.17,1:41:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！少年！
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.74,1:41:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去開拓未來吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.32,1:41:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.49,1:41:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 QAN[T] 已經進去了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.17,1:41:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.36,1:41:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 提艾利亞
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.25,1:41:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 污染情況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.02,1:41:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過15%了！
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.49,1:41:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦艦隊的損失為55%
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.16,1:41:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九條
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.15,1:42:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱蒂 再堅持一會
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.91,1:42:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有勝算嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.84,1:42:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.36,1:42:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.02,1:42:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有希望！
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.34,1:42:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.12,1:42:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還沒完
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.97,1:42:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.50,1:42:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.14,1:42:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.09,1:42:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.52,1:42:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也要去！
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.97,1:43:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種行為就叫做偽善
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.26,1:43:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.32,1:43:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再見死不救了！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.25,1:43:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.29,1:43:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.99,1:43:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用TRANS-AM衝入ELS的中樞
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.66,1:43:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.60,1:43:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM是進行對話的王牌
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.41,1:43:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在這裡用
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.54,1:43:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.45,1:43:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那！
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.13,1:44:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣把它切開！
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.43,1:44:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年！
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.34,1:44:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶你通向未來的領航員
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.83,1:44:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我古拉哈姆·艾卡來做吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.80,1:44:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.32,1:44:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了人類的生存！
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.48,1:44:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.65,1:44:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.54,1:44:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝進去！
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.31,1:45:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 QAN[T] 看來已經衝進ELS的中樞了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.17,1:45:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦的污染情況如何
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.12,1:45:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經超過44%了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.78,1:45:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力場已經無法展開了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.44,1:45:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是…做棄艦的準備…
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.47,1:45:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.25,1:45:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想像克麗絲蒂娜那時一樣 自己留下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.68,1:45:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.95,1:45:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要大家都活下去！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.41,1:45:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜也要留下來！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.49,1:45:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在放棄還太早了！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.48,1:45:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們堅信到最後吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.18,1:45:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.69,1:45:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是…
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.49,1:45:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.73,1:45:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要開拓
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.08,1:45:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.02,1:45:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有明日！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.80,1:45:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 去相信吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.84,1:45:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信剎那吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.91,1:46:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊 損失70%了！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.25,1:46:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.81,1:46:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…ELS的中樞？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.23,1:46:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在迎接我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.47,1:46:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備啟動量子系統
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.47,1:46:43.09,eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1093,990)}QUANTUM SYSTEM
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.94,1:46:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS的力量還是未知數 用盡全力！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.90,1:46:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.93,1:46:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子爆發！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.93,1:46:52.31,eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(899,990)}QUANTUM BURST
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.56,1:47:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後的任務！
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.45,1:47:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上人類的存亡
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.48,1:47:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始對話！
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.39,1:47:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想理解
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.34,1:47:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想互相理解
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.33,1:47:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.57,1:47:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能互相理解
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.13,1:47:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ELS的意識…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.40,1:47:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我連接吧 剎那
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.27,1:47:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個信息洪流 就由我和維塔來接收
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.53,1:47:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開多餘的東西 去理解它們的本質
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.70,1:47:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的感受！
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.28,1:49:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.22,1:50:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的母星正在走向死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.77,1:50:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們正在尋找生存之路嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.36,1:50:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們互相連結 合為一體
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.12,1:50:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後互相理解
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.75,1:50:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去它們的母星
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.75,1:50:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有必要和它們互相理解
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.64,1:50:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.81,1:50:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好不好的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.87,1:50:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是對我來說
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.16,1:50:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.76,1:50:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.71,1:50:29.00,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}對不起 米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.00,1:50:31.86,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不行！我要和爸爸媽媽在一起！
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.70,1:50:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.15,1:50:33.56,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}讓我去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.16,1:50:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.58,1:50:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為何我們的想法會不同
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.83,1:50:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為我們擁有智慧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.82,1:50:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使是瑣碎的事情也會引起誤會
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.08,1:50:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後形成謊言 將我們區別開
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.98,1:50:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我們最終無法互相理解
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.94,1:50:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是艾鈕 最後都互相理解了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.68,1:51:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你們也一定…
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.23,1:51:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是沒有發現
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.48,1:51:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我們一定要為大家指出
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.05,1:51:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界本來…
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.42,1:51:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此簡單
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.47,1:51:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 ELS聚集起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.01,1:51:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.94,1:51:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.14,1:51:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來了…
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.80,1:51:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利 快看
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.26,1:51:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼現象
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.37,1:51:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.64,1:51:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.84,1:51:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.70,1:51:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.85,1:51:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了哦 剎那
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.42,1:52:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.70,1:52:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 只需如此
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.70,1:52:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以將世界融為一體了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.44,1:57:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了能傳達意識的新型原始粒子
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.30,1:57:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構築了能製造這種粒子的半永動裝置的基礎理論
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.25,1:57:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發明量子型運算系統
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.41,1:57:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建造軌道電梯
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.50,1:57:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提倡太陽能發電系統
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.96,1:57:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪個都是能讓我們人類變得更繁榮的技術
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.65,1:57:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你很討厭人類
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.91,1:57:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個孤島上一個人生活
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.22,1:57:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所討厭的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.20,1:57:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是錯誤地使用智慧
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.17,1:57:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為固執和先入為主
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.57,1:57:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而無法看到真實的人
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.43,1:57:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會帶來誤解
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.07,1:57:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來不和
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.33,1:57:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.39,1:57:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望…人們能互相理解
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.59,1:57:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你所追求的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.08,1:58:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類要正確地使用智慧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.49,1:58:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須要進化
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.40,1:58:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話 就算向宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.14,1:58:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著更廣闊的世界進發
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.56,1:58:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會燃起新的火種
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.51,1:58:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那將是非常悲哀的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.69,1:58:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞…
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.19,1:58:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位請看！
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.46,1:58:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球聯邦軍引以為豪的最新型外太空航行艦
Dialogue: 0,1:58:29.65,1:58:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「皇」的雄姿
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.88,1:58:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數小時後 這艘船就會駛向外太空
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.54,1:58:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開漫長的旅程
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.82,1:58:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成員為了可以承受長時間的航程
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.70,1:58:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都由變革者組成
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.21,1:58:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 全人類裡有四成是變革者
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.05,1:58:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們能解決各種問題
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.21,1:58:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也終於迎來這個時刻了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.80,1:58:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會作為專屬特派員
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.77,1:58:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這艘船一起出發航行
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.51,1:59:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後會盡我所能 將信息帶給各位
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.93,1:59:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請各位聽聽統領這1200名船員的最高負責人
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.12,1:59:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯·格拉德的談話
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.87,1:59:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位…呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.72,1:59:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.27,1:59:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這眼…不太好…
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.52,1:59:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.78,1:59:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.08,1:59:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.89,1:59:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來 我花了很長的時間
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.49,1:59:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我們想法不同而已…
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.05,1:59:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們所追求的東西是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.99,2:00:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.50,2:00:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正確的
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.43,2:00:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是…沒有做錯…
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.53,2:00:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於…
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.29,2:00:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於…
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.28,2:00:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以互相理解了
